Of course, one can improve Lemma~\ref{thm:multi_size_ram_Pn} slightly. For example, in the first step there is no need to assume that the graph is bipartite. Also one could try to use the ``double wholes'' approach as in Lemma~\ref{lem:2_colours}. However, the improvement would not be substantial. It would be interesting to determine the order of magnitude of ${\hat{R}({{P_n,r}})}$ as a function of $r$ (for fixed $n$). 

